    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who advocate the extension or granting of political suffrage to those lacking it, either universally or to specific groups within the population.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
